## Add

**Description:** Add device to the database

**Address:** localhost:port/device/add

**Request Type:** POST

**API Parameters:**

|No|Name|Data Type|IsRequired|Sample|Description|Note|
|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|
|1|maker|String|Yes|Maker7|Device Maker||
|2|model|String|Yes|Model7|Device model||
|3|measurement|String|Yes|temperature|Measurement type of the device||
|4|measurement_unit|String|Yes|Â°C|Unit of the measurement||



**Result:**

Data Type: Text

|No|Name|Data Type|IsRequired|Sample|Description|Note|
|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|
|1|body|String|Yes|Successfully add new device|Result of response||



**Result Sample:**
```
Successfully add new device
```